  "prompt": "Does Palantir give its employees raises?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, Palantir Technologies, like many companies, may offer raises to its employees based on performance reviews, promotion criteria, market adjustments, and company financial health. Typically, the specifics of compensation adjustments, including raises, are determined internally and may vary from one employee to another. However, details about the frequency, percentage increase, and criteria for raises are usually not publicly disclosed and can depend on the role, location, and individual performance. For the most accurate and up-to-date information, it would be best to refer directly to Palantir's HR policies or speak to someone within the company.",
